data.name: TextBox3.Text
data.value: We are a family owned business with 6 kids and a passion for all things with an engine. With 28 years of experience, we have built over two dozen baja and trophy trucks, and have had the privilege of working with industry legends such as Nitro Circus, Brian Deegan, Ricky Johnson, and many more. Our dedication and expertise in the world of motorsports is unparalleled, and we strive to provide top-notch service and performance in everything we do.

data.name: TextBox4.Text
data.value: Elias Flores grew up in the rough and unforgiving neighborhood of O'block, where violence and poverty were a part of daily life. Despite the struggles and hardships he faced growing up, Elias always dreamed of a better future for himself and his community. After graduating, Elias founded his own company called Motion Design and Development, with a mission to provide innovative solutions and opportunities for underserved communities like the one he came from. He poured all of his time, energy, and resources into building his company, determined to make a positive impact on the world around him.
